{"tid":1280449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【明日香港】報道指中國秘密掃瞄前往新疆遊客手機","createTime":"2019-07-03T03:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T06:37:45.000Z","uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d935e37dfa636159b408def1e4d4a9148ff2668","tid":1280449,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"報道指中國秘密掃瞄前往新疆遊客手機<br />\n2019/07/03<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有報道指，中國邊防人員在旅客的手機秘密安裝手機應用程式，監視前往新疆的遊客。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》和美國《紐約時報》等傳媒進行的聯合調查報道指出，由鄰近中亞地區，以陸路進入新疆的旅客，被中國邊防人員要求交出手機檢查時，邊防人員會在不作知會的情況下，為手機下載一個名為「蜂采」的應用程式，以掃瞄和檢查手機內的電郵、短訊、照片、短片和聯絡人等資料，是否涉及敏感內容。<br />\n<br />\n有關應用程式會比對一個牽涉超過七萬三千個敏感內容項目的清單，清單中包括極端組織伊斯蘭國刊物、達賴喇嘛照片、可蘭經文錄音等。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，在大部分情況，邊防人員向旅客歸還手機前，會將應用程式刪除，暫未清楚中方在旅客手機獲得的資料會傳往哪裏，以及會儲存多久。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kHHBgni.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkHHBgni.png&h=dc3dd54b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=354008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354008&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsIhk9ljSbOzVJb7ECUhiv3w%3D&h=eead56e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354008&h=8a7c9f1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=354008</a>"},{"pid":"94240207ab4f238d8f5cc9c86c6d85665530235d","tid":1280449,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9cf780e54a94019a7d5fcd44d1a8564fc3d3d0f","tid":1280449,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:43:40.000Z","msg":"btw, 點解會有人夠膽去新疆旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14a757d72693ab1b3fb9e439156ed11b7a2d13ab","tid":1280449,"uid":51436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime